  "title": "EEG frequency tagging reveals the integration of dissimilar observed actions",
  "description": "This dataset contains EEG recordings from an experiment investigating how the brain integrates dissimilar observed actions using frequency tagging methodology. Participants viewed action stimuli while EEG was recorded to measure neural responses at specific frequency tags, revealing neural mechanisms of action integration and observation.",
